# NeuroDraft loads env from each Next.js app separately.
#
#   • Main app (API keys):  copy `app/.env.example` → `app/.env.local`
#   • Marketing site:       copy `landing/.env.example` → `landing/.env.local`
#
# Committed `*.env.production` files only set public URLs for deploys; secrets stay in
# the host’s env or in `.env.local` locally (never committed).
